  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they call you, you go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they don't call you, don't be-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] don't go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't volunteer?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't be a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to go, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- so I did not go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by Friday night, and that was Tuesday night, then-- Wednesday night, Thursday night, and Friday night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By Friday night, there were left about 200, 300 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did not ship it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had the Saturday was the free day in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Poland, we worked, but in Germany, they had a free day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they shipped us home by Friday night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, very-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Practically nothing two days you can survive without feeding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is why I wanted to go, because I wasn't fed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was thirsty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You lay on your face, you pee under yourself here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't move for 48 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is why, when every time they called, I said, I'm going!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said, no, you lay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So until they don't call you by the name, you don't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you leave it to the action, but you don't do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you, for these 40, this is why you wanted to be-- to go by yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then what happened when you were released?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a different time than today, because by Friday night, my mother's seeing, finally gathered we are in Czwartakow, went even after the hours.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After 8 o'clock, you couldn't go out the street for anybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was wartime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she went there, because on that idea, they will not touch a woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody's going to touch a woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she went.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
